Package: HSMap
Type: Package
Title: Map Construction in Half-Sib Populations
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: c(
    person(
      "Marcelo", "Mollinari",
      email = "mmollina@gmail.com",
      role = c("aut", "cre")
    )
  )
Description: A fast C++ (Rcpp) implementation that uses a two-state Hidden 
             Markov Model to estimate recombination rates between genetic 
             markers from offspring genotypes in outcrossing diploid species. 
             It handles known mothers, optional known sires,   multiple 
             populations (families), and scattered missing markers.
